sql: SELECT DATE_TRUNC('month', bookingdate) AS month, COUNT(CASE WHEN booking_status='IssuedBusiness' THEN 1 END) as bookings FROM sme_analytics.sme_leadbookingrevenue WHERE investmenttypeid IN (13) AND DATE(bookingdate) >= DATE '2025-01-01' AND DATE(bookingdate) <= DATE '2025-12-31' GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('month', bookingdate)
